        {
            "title": "大埔公路6車相撞｜車cam直擊撞車驚悚一刻 七人車「彈起」冒煙碎片四散",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/80ed8834067371f0bf8f36a5e8aa0102/732db3de0f2949aeb228666e4333a5ec-da814f6c7a1bedb4e3166d4515628726-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67dd985ce4497\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67dd985ce4498\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/02786b15a0821951b27846de9ece1963/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032200430892747.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>大埔公路今日（21日）晚上發生6車相撞意外，一名目睹車禍經過的司機向《星島頭條》表示，事發時一輛被警方追截的七人車逆線行駛，幸他及時收油扭軚，避過一劫，「當然係瘋狂駕駛啦‥‥當下收油扭左少少，如果唔係佢就撞到我，當然係停車定一定驚啦，搞唔掂呀」。\n\n</p>\n<p>市民蘇先生表示，當時他沿大埔公路往九龍方向行駛，準備回家休息，突然有一輛車頭已經損毀的七人車迎面駛至，「佢逆線緊行駛，差啲撞埋嚟㗎啦，當下收油扭左少少，佢就無撞到我，但就撞左我後面嗰架Tesla」。他指當時七人車撞到兩輛車後始停下，司機立即棄車逃走，惟警方迅速到場將他制服。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3439958/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%85%AC%E8%B7%AF6%E8%BB%8A%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E%E9%87%805%E5%82%B7-%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%BB%8A%E6%B6%89%E7%8B%82%E4%BA%82%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA\" target=\"_blank\">大埔公路6車相撞釀5傷 七人車涉狂亂駕駛 警拘兩人</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>根據蘇先生提供的車cam片段所見，七人車撞到其他車後整架「彈起」，碎片四散，現場隨即冒出白煙。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151928/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蘇先生。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9bc032ababd63f60ab7289982b9870b0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_224744489.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蘇先生。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151934/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蘇先生的座駕未有損毀。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb3996ea709a61f5081fad02374ee54f/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_224659618_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蘇先生的座駕未有損毀。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151929/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a174e670e30c532a3fb4c3ae1592e191/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_224708423_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151930/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/58a5521bf557e912d6150cdad06e5475/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_224707131_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151927/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方封鎖現場調查。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02eb46b975c39c9d77dda030bf7a6300/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_230637014.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方封鎖現場調查。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151926/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/29aa7ac6fbe90aea300dfd42bff2c1b9/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_230638433.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151933/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ccf00410ffadb86a3ea164127e700939/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_224658191_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151932/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f98f1945613ca5733e36530bbaac37a5/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_224659618.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大埔公路發生6車相撞意外。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151931/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"有私家車車身嚴重損毀。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4d130c9fdbba6b51b5726f7a230b0cc6/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_224704169_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有私家車車身嚴重損毀。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=