            "title": "大埔公路6車相撞‧車cam直擊｜七人車逃避警方追截 一度切雙白線逆線狂飆",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/a0dff6ac066171f0bf914177d1c00102/c06e4c4d4ccb4794a4eddef2fcaf5590-c21128926f0e7959e688315395597a5f-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67dd868385c14\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67dd868385c19\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7ae174d1352fdab1049435add7aa4a69/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032123280146329.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> 大埔公路沙田段今日（21日）發生6車相撞意外，造成5人受傷。據了解，一輛七人車疑因衝燈問題而被警方追截，駛至徑口路交界時與多輛車發生相撞。事後網上有一段車cam影片流出，清楚見到七人車為逃避警方追截，一度切雙白線逆線行駛，幾乎與迎頭駛至的私家車及電單車相撞，非常牙煙。\n\n</p>\n<p>車cam片段的左上角顯示事發時間為今日晚上8時58分。一輛七人車當時在大埔公路高速飛馳，其間更逆線行駛，幾乎與迎頭駛至的私家車及電單車相撞，一輛警車響鞍緊隨其後，雙方展開「追遂戰」，車cam片主更驚訝表示：「勁呀！馬騮山逆線呀！」\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3439958/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%85%AC%E8%B7%AF6%E8%BB%8A%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E%E9%87%805%E5%82%B7-%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%BB%8A%E6%B6%89%E7%8B%82%E4%BA%82%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA\">大埔公路6車相撞釀5傷 七人車涉狂亂駕駛 警拘兩人</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151917/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛七人車高速在大埔公路飛馳，甚至一度逆線行駛。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4ec3a5885eb0fe3e099d21485f3c651e/2025-03/WhatsApp_Video_2025-03-21_at_22_06_22_mp4_snapshot_00_02_282.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛七人車高速在大埔公路飛馳，甚至一度逆線行駛。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151916/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛七人車高速在大埔公路飛馳，甚至一度逆線行駛。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0f3cc86bd47f0ec6da63165aa015f3b5/2025-03/WhatsApp_Video_2025-03-21_at_22_06_22_mp4_snapshot_00_02_631.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛七人車高速在大埔公路飛馳，甚至一度逆線行駛。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151915/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛七人車高速在大埔公路飛馳，甚至一度逆線行駛。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/01a503eae5533da6acc1baabbc31ebd6/2025-03/WhatsApp_Video_2025-03-21_at_22_06_22_mp4_snapshot_00_03_532.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛七人車高速在大埔公路飛馳，甚至一度逆線行駛。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151914/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"七人車切雙白線。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/667252c5355f60dbad120d306bd9e7cb/2025-03/WhatsApp_Video_2025-03-21_at_22_06_23_mp4_snapshot_00_00_438.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        七人車切雙白線。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151913/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛警車尾隨七人車。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2dd69a3f036f9c2d4b3f56f0bef96092/2025-03/WhatsApp_Video_2025-03-21_at_22_06_23_mp4_snapshot_00_01_469.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛警車尾隨七人車。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059584/即時-港聞-大埔公路6車相撞-車cam直擊-七人車逃避警方追截-一度切雙白線逆線狂飆",
