            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "泰峯加推98伙 入場價408萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"泰峯加推98伙，入場價408萬。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/eee676c5b16d502934278abd319c0d9e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032122575281871.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">泰峯加推98伙，入場價408萬。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>王新興集團發展的九龍灣新盤泰峯，剛加推98伙，面積由279至501方呎，屬開放式至2房，價單定價約530.48萬至1,128萬元，呎價19,011至23,654元，扣除23%折扣，折實售價約408.4萬至868.6萬元，折實呎價約14,638至18,214元。\n\n</p>\n<p>同時上載銷售安排，將於下周二價單連同招標單位推售178伙，包括98伙價單單位，以及80伙招標單位。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
